```
#!/bin/bash
date
echo "Starting clean netgo data"

echo "Cleaning summary"
mysql -uroot -p123@123 netgo -e "DELETE FROM summary WHERE created_at < DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 3 MONTH);"
echo "Cleaned summary"

echo "Cleaning tracking"
mysql -uroot -p123@123 netgo -e "DELETE FROM tracking WHERE created_at < DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 3 MONTH);"
echo "Cleaned tracking"

echo "Cleaning access_tracking"
mysql -uroot -p123@123 netgo -e "DELETE FROM access_tracking WHERE created_at < DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 2 MONTH);"
echo "Cleaned"

echo "Optimizing summary"
mysql -uroot -p123@123 netgo -e "OPTIMIZE TABLES summary;"
echo "Optimized"

echo "Optimizing tracking"
mysql -uroot -p123@123 netgo -e "OPTIMIZE TABLES tracking;"
echo "Optimized"

echo "Optimizing access_tracking"
mysql -uroot -p123@123 netgo -e "OPTIMIZE TABLES access_tracking;"
echo "Optimizing"

echo "Clear old logs"
rm -f /etc/httpd/logs/access_log-*

date
echo "Program completed!"
```

2. Tương tự 1 sp có đơn thì cần bộ phận xử lý đơn hàng (để xử lý đơn đó). Bộ phận mua hàng tương lai thì có cần nhập thêm sp đó k?
